---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout includeHeading subtitle="Media">
  <section id="media">
    <article>
      <p>
        My experience as an artist continues to develop with my work on the web. If you're interested in learning about
        my winding path from music and education to code, I gave a
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u76CKtRjgq0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2022 tech talk</a>
        on how making music led me to pursue a future in code in collaboration with
        <a href="https://the-collab-lab.codes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Collab Lab</a>, which you can view
        below.
      </p>
    </article>
    <figure>
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/u76CKtRjgq0"
        title="YouTube video player"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </figure>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  figure {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 2rem;
  }
  iframe {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
  }
</style>
